## Configuration

All configuration is centralized in `pyproject.toml`:

- **Build system**: Hatchling
- **Dependencies**: Core and optional (dev, docs)
- **Ruff**: Linting and formatting rules
- **mypy**: Type checking configuration
- **pytest**: Test discovery and coverage settings

## Continuous Integration & Development

This repository includes a GitHub Actions workflow located at `.github/workflows/ci.yml` that runs:
- Tests with pytest and coverage
- Ruff linting and formatting checks
- mypy type checking
- Bandit security scanning

All checks run on Python 3.13 by default.

